# FitTrack Pro - Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your values.

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------
# Google Fit API Key
# Required for the Health Sync feature (Google Fit integration).
# Steps to obtain:
#   1. Go to https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials
#   2. Create a new project (or select an existing one).
#   3. Enable the "Fitness API" under APIs & Services > Library.
#   4. Create an API key under APIs & Services > Credentials.
#   5. (Recommended) Restrict the key to the Fitness API and your domain.
# Prefix NEXT_PUBLIC_ makes this value available in the browser bundle.
# Do NOT commit your actual key -- add .env.local to .gitignore.
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------
NEXT_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_FIT_API_KEY=your_google_fit_api_key_here
